### User anlegen
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "Max Mustermann",
  "distinctName": "max_m",
  "email": "max.mustermann@test.at",
  "biography": "Neuer User"
}

?? status == 201


